<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="a4Mar1931"><font color="red">4 March 1931</font> <i>Letters I</i> (to Harriet Weaver, typed): &hellip; to say nothing of arranging all my correspondence and notes and trying to follow with various readers the books I am using for the present fragment which include Marie Corelli, Swedenborg, St Thomas, the Sudanese war, Indian outcasts, Women under English Law, a description of St. Helena, Flammarion&apos;s The End of the World, scores of children&apos;s singing games from Germany, France, England and Italy and so on </div>
